chapter:
&reftitle.setup;




 &reftitle.required;


  This extension uses the functions of the 
  FAM library, developed by SGI. Therefore you have to download and
  install the FAM library.





&reference.fam.configure;





 &reftitle.runtime;
 &no.config;






 &reftitle.resources;


  There are two resource types used in the FAM module. The first one is
  the connection to the FAM service returned by 
  fam_open, the second a monitoring resource returned
  by the fam_monitor_XXX functions.
